leads.lead_text: Leaves narrow-lanceolate, more or less obtuse, venation obscure; calyx prominently lobed; petals imbricate in bud; fruit globose, 6–10 mm diam
Leaves ovate to lanceolate, acuminate, distinctly reticulate-veined on both sur-faces; calyx obscurely lobed; petals induplicate-valvate in bud; fruit ellipsoid-ovoid, 15–20 mm long
